    {
        "url": "/quotes/fernando_botero_756573",
        "quote": "Art is important because when people start to forget, art reminds them what happened. Like 'Guernica.' People would not remember the tragedy of Guernica today if it were not for that painting.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Fernando Botero",
            "url": "/quotes/fernando_botero_756573"
