    {
        "url": "/quotes/fernando_botero_756594",
        "quote": "All my life, my girlfriends are always skinny. Beauty in art has nothing to do with beauty in reality. Why do you like primitive art? Because there is beauty in the deformity. Sometimes paintings that people consider realistic are not at all. Raphael figures look realistic, but in real life, they were deformed.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Fernando Botero",
            "url": "/quotes/fernando_botero_756594"
