        "url": "/quotes/fernando_botero_756586",
        "quote": "Bullfights have so much color. Not just the matador but also the bull, the arena, and the public. It's all very festive.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Fernando Botero",
            "url": "/quotes/fernando_botero_756586"
